    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Urban Planning\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan out new features for the city using **text, images, and a city planning report**.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Upload one of the **aerial images** of city layouts from the Library.\r\n2. Upload **one** of the following **Planning Document PDFs** from the Library:\r\n\r\n::: details [**City Zoning Guide**]\r\nHelps consider land use and regulations.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Transit Report**]\r\nHighlights areas needing better accessibility.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Urban Development Plan**]\r\nShows upcoming projects and growth strategies.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n3. **Modify the following prompt** for the image and document you chose and press **Send**:\r\n\r\n>Analyze this image and document. What are some possible improvements for **[insert category: transportation, green spaces, zoning, safety, or another of your choice]** in this area? Justify your recommendations.\r\n\r\n4. Read AI Chat's response.\r\n5. **Experiment**: Test how AI responds to different inputs:\r\n   - **Modify your prompt** to focus on a different urban feature.\r\n   - **Change your input document or image** to see how AI’s response shifts.\r\n\r\n---\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I upload an file?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Upload** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Library**\r\n- Then browse the existing files.\r\n- When you have a file to upload, click the checkbox next to it to select it and then click **Open**.\r\n- You should see the file(s) get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n",
